.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-FEE-EARNED-TOTAL" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-fee-earned-total \- FEAT-2533 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-fee-earned-total
.SH DESCRIPTION
peer-fee-earned-total for lightning CLI (FEAT-2533).
.PP
Returns the sum of fee_msat earned per peer across their channels.
Output: JSON from CLN with key fee_earned_total_msat.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
